        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Exodus 40:21-29",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", which makes it clear that the altar was placed with the golden candlestick and the table of shew-bread, outside the veil, in the \"holy place,\" and not within the  \"holy of holies.\" ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Where I will meet with",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
